"Yes... I'm... okay now. Sorry, Ishii, I can't talk about the details yet..."[l][r]
"Oh... okay. No worries. I'm sorry for confusing you... for making things worse."[r]
That’s right. There’s no way we can discuss all our experiences in that harsh world over the phone.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

